title: Ep. 111 - Happy Belated Indigenous Peoples’ Day
description:
Everyone knows that this is an educational podcast and this episode is no exception. The boys teach you all about Christopher Columbus and his contributions to the world. They also ripped through some great listener questions that caused them to travel back in time.

Bonus content: At the end of this episode is the 3rd episode of How’s It Smell? They reviewed El Camino.
